flowchart TD
    subgraph Cliente[Browser / App]
        A[Login 2FA] -->|sendText direto| WA[whatsappAutoService]

        B[Modal S-89: cartao individual] -->|MANUAL: clipboard + WhatsApp Web| MAN[generateWhatsAppUrl]
        B -->|Z-API: botao S-89 z-api| ORC[zapiOrchestrator]
        C[Modal S-89: reconfirmacao] -->|MANUAL| MAN
        D[Modal S-89: S-140/Status z-api] -->|getBroadcastRecipients + dispatchImageToRecipients| ORC

        E[Portal: publicador ACEITA] -->|dispatchS89Receipt| ORC
        F[Portal: publicador RECUSA] -->|dispatchRefusalAlert| ORC

        P1[Aba Apostila: Publicar / Despublicar semana] --> WPS[weekPublishService]
        P2[Agente: /publicar, /despublicar + chip] --> WPS
        WPS -->|S-89 lote idempotente PUBLICACAO_S89| ORC
        WPS -->|S-140 + Status board headless ao broadcast| ORC
    end

    subgraph Servidor
        CRON[pg_cron 09:00 BRT] -->|x-cron-secret| REM[cron-whatsapp-reminders]
        REM -->|D-7/D-2/D-1| EF[send-whatsapp]
        ORC --> EF
        WA --> EF
        EF -->|client-token| ZAPI[(Z-API REST)]
    end

    MAN -.->|abre WhatsApp Web, humano cola| Humano

    BC([Destinatarios broadcast = Ajd SRVM + SRVM + Grupo])
    D -.-> BC
    WPS -.-> BC

